# Static Web Project Standards

- Keep the site deployable as static assets with no server dependency.
- Prefer semantic HTML structure and clear, accessible call-to-action text.
- Never commit credentials or secrets; use environment variables only.
- Run `npm run quality` before opening PRs.
- Keep styles in `assets/styles.css` or additional modular CSS files.

## Build

- Build to `dist/` with `npm run build`; publish that directory to the static host.
